1) Compiling

make

2) Installing

make install

3) Generate host key

as root:
# mkdir /etc/ssc
# rsagen 2048 /etc/ssc/host-priv /etc/ssc/host-pub

4) Generate private key

rsagen -h 2048

5 Start daemon as

tcpd tcpmux tcpmux sscp /usr/local/bin/sscserver sscserver


